  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育评估流程画一个状态图。核心是从GradeSync系统发起一个Avalúo（评估请求），然后经过一系列分配和审核步骤，最终数据写入StudentDB。起点是SinAsignar状态，终点是Completado。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "SinAsignar",
        "Avalúo",
        "Completado",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以GradeSync创建Avalúo后进入SinAsignar。接下来是谁来分配？是Manager直接分配给Colegio，还是先有一个中间环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SinAsignar",
        "Manager",
        "Colegio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Manager分配给Colegio，状态变为AsignadoColegio。然后Colegio的代表再分配给具体的Perito（评估专家），进入AsignadoPerito状态。Perito确认接受后才真正开始工作，进入EnProgreso。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "Colegio",
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "Perito",
        "EnProgreso"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前半部分画出来：GradeSync → SinAsignar → AsignadoColegio → AsignadoPerito → EnProgreso。接下来EnProgreso之后是什么？直接完成吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "SinAsignar",
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "EnProgreso"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，Perito完成工作后提交，进入EnRevision（审核中）。这里需要分支：如果审核通过，就到Completado；如果需要修改，要回到Observaciones状态，Perito修正后再回到EnProgreso。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EnProgreso",
        "EnRevision",
        "Completado",
        "Observaciones"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下流程：EnRevision如果通过就到Completado；如果需要修改，先到Observaciones，然后Perito修正后回到EnProgreso重新提交。这个循环我理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EnRevision",
        "Completado",
        "Observaciones",
        "EnProgreso",
        "Perito"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，完全正确。最后Completado状态的数据要写入Education_StudentDB。整个流程是单向的，只有Observaciones那里有一个回到EnProgreso的循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Completado",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Observaciones",
        "EnProgreso"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我画出了全部状态：从GradeSync创建Avalúo开始，经过Manager分配、Colegio分配、Perito接受、工作进行中、提交审核，分支处理修改意见或批准完成，最终数据落地到StudentDB。",
